{
  "stem": "19923.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were told if anyone spoke a word of German in the presence of the French soldiers, we would-- we'd be put on bread and water for eight days.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Unfortunately, my French was not so good because I'd only lived in Belgium for a year and a half.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I spoke mostly German and my French improved while I was in southern France.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I got caught speaking a German word or saying something in German and I was put on bread and water for eight days.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was my-- my first experience of the harsh life in southern France.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I say bread and water for eight days, I mean two slices of bread a day.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's all I had to eat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, we didn't have much to eat anyways because most of us were scrounging around in the-- the neighborhood, the farm area, and the farmers were too kind to us.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If they saw us going on one of their fig trees or apple trees, they'd shoot at you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't want you there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I became quite adept at being able to forage for food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I could smell where a potato was being grown.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I could dig up a potato-- a raw potato, brush it off with my hand, eat it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I could do the same with onions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I knew when the onions were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So just foraging around and scrounging around helped you being able to survive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was very little food that was available in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We just did as best we could.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I do have a recollection of going to the blacksmith one day in the village.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the blacksmith had made himself some toast and I guess he blackened it too much and discarded it.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
